    This test class holds the unit tests regarding the administration pages and actions
    AnonymousControllerTest
    This test class holds tests against all the protected controllers methods performed by an anonymous user Most of the tests are expecting to get an "Access Denied" response.
    ConcreteAuthentication
    Class used to emulate an authentication with Spring Security in order to be able to run some test cases as different user profiles.
